head: <!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><style>body {font-family: arial, sans-serif;max-width: 1200px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top: 0;}table {width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;text-align: left;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: grey;}th,td {padding: 8px;}th {border-color: #616161;background-color: #616161;color: white;}th:hover {background-color: #333333;}td {border-color: #dddddd;}tr:nth-child(even) {background-color: #dddddd;}tr:hover td {background-color: #24a204;border-color: #24a204;color: white;}@media (max-width: 40em) {section {margin: 0px;}}@media (min-width: 40em) {section {margin: 20px;}}<//style><link rel="stylesheet" href="styles_static.css">
